            "<p><strong>8.1</strong> MGS issues an invoice for each payment demand that lists the services in detail and complies with tax regulations. Unless otherwise agreed, the following payment terms apply: 7 days net, without discount. In case of disputes, the undisputed portion must be paid.</p>",
