            "<p><strong>10.3</strong> Defective goods or parts will, at MGS's discretion, be repaired or replaced. The place of performance for defect rectification is MGS's premises unless otherwise contractually agreed. Additional costs will be borne by the customer.</p>",
            "<p><strong>10.4</strong> MGS's liability period is 6 months from the time of service or transfer of risk. The cause must predate the transfer of risk and result from poor construction, inferior materials, or defective workmanship.</p>",
