            "<h2>11. Confidentiality / Data Protection</h2>",
            "<p><strong>11.1</strong> The customer is informed in accordance with Section 33, Paragraph 1 of the Federal Data Protection Act that MGS stores customer data in machine-readable form for customer care purposes and contract-related tasks.</p>",
